title: Saturday Night Live Season 23 Complete
description:
SNL Season 23 (1997-1998)

The 23rd SEASON OF SATURDAY NIGHT LIVE.

ALL THE SKETCHES AND ALL THE LAUGHTER.

ONE OF THE SNL CAST MEMBER:CHRIS FARLEY HOST THE OCTOBER 26th 1997. SHOW. FOR ONE LAST TIME ON THE SHOW. JUST BEFORE HIS DEATH 2 MONTHS LATER.

AND IT WAS ALSO NORM McDONALD'S LAST SEASON ON THE SHOW. DURING THE SEASON NORM McDONALD GOT FIRED FROM WEEKEND UPDATE AND SNL. AND IT WAS REPLACED BY COLIN QUINN DOING THE WEEKEND UPDATE A FEW SHOWS LATER.

SO HERE IS SEASON 23 OF SATURDAY NIGHT LIVE
